title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 35000
description:
OK Gang getting close to the point where I will be re seeding the letter M under a new torrent name due to the error I made a few months ago.   I would recommend you delete all the letter M you downloaded and start again as I have added new files and altered the title string on a lot of songs to include multiple Karaoke Label choice.

As I go along I am also re ripping the original CD's to give better audio quality.

PLEASE NOTE that after this letter the collection will have more duplicates and errors as this is work in progress and takes a lot of my time.

Rigmar Radio - Seeding to the World since 2004
